Notes: NU started out on a 7-0 run... built an 11-pt lead (16-5) at the 11:37 mark...
CSC cut the lead to five (27-22) with 2:08 to play... NU leads 33-23 at half.
CSC opens the 2nd half by cutting the lead to five (35-30) at 18:27 mark... NU
then goes on a 14-2 run for a 12-pt lead and goes on to the 56-46 win.
